    "17672098": {
      "title": "Planar embeddings with a globally attracting fixed point",
      "abstract": "Abstract We consider sufficient conditions which guarantee that an embedding from the plane R 2 into itself has a unique fixed point. We subsequently study sufficient conditions under which there appears a globally attracting fixed point for such an embedding."
    }
